{"tid":945566,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"思捷環球 0330.hk 無得輸!","createTime":"2018-12-18T03:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T04:26:29.000Z","uid":53062,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b082a3d935087dd0de7d7d51447639bda83b8bc1","tid":945566,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T03:57:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://forum.hkej.com/node/92948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkej.com%2Fnode%2F92948&d=IZf6lr%2BCsfQX4MnErcdNIYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=bfb92604\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkej.com/node/92948</a><br />\n<br />\n思捷環球 <a href=\"http://0330.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F0330.hk&d=IZf6lr%2BCsfQX4MnErcdNIYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=57c3522d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">0330.hk</a> 無得輸! 因為已經輸到盡，由07-08年高位120蚊，挫到最底7蚊，最高位至最底位跌覆達94%，重有得輸? &quot;電盈都係咁啦，一跌無回頭&quot;，電盈無回頭既原因係當年開放電訊牌照，由壟斷變左要同其他電訊商競爭，更係無番生啦，但係時裝不嬲都有兢爭對手，所以唔可以同電盈雙題並論。<br />\n<br />\n思捷環球 <a href=\"http://0330.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F0330.hk&d=IZf6lr%2BCsfQX4MnErcdNIYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=57c3522d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">0330.hk</a> 跌既原因係歐債危機遲遲未了，繼而將焦點轉到品派老化所造成。隨歐債危機慢慢淡化，思捷基地-德國撐歐盟同歐央行無限救市請救歐元等等，有理由相信思捷無得輸(再輸)。<br />\n<br />\n思捷環球請人<br />\n<br />\nRonald van der Vis 與 Jose Manuel Martinez Gutierrez<br />\n<br />\nRonald van der Vis - 呢個舊CEO，可以話係求其請，完全無代表作，最後只係係德國科隆開左間Esprit concept store, 同埋用一個歐洲model做代言人，D廣告就想全世界用，屣氣啦。人地H&amp;M用Macdonna先可以全世界用咋!最後Esprit終於明白請人的重要性，請左Jose Manuel Martinez Gutierrez, 前Inditex(即Zara)管理層，42歲，彌補管理層老化至品牌老化問題，Zara有幾成功，無須多講，時裝既趨勢就係Fast Fashion, 大家見foever21, H&amp;M, Zara, 等等, 就係呢類。<br />\n<br />\n思捷網點全球數千間，呢個係重要資產，而思捷多年於行內經驗，貨原成本亦懇定好過很多品牌。現在個Brand輸晒，無得再輸，所以只要做番好個Brand，做好Marketing，先不吝昔租金，關店於人流小的地方，開店於人流高的地方，打好品牌，D buyer行多D H&amp;M同Zara, 入D有質數既貨，及投放資源於國內店鋪，認真搞番好個網站(現在仲係唔掂), Window Display 等等, 思捷環球 <a href=\"http://0330.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F0330.hk&d=IZf6lr%2BCsfQX4MnErcdNIYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=57c3522d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">0330.hk</a> 上升空間仍非常高。<br />\n<br />\n那些年, ESPRIT品牌係潮既象徵，於times square那間店，女生每次見到都會o艾 &quot;ESPRIT 呀..&quot;, Red Earth花粧品及入ESPRIT剪頭髮亦係學生哥既夢想, 有個同學享ESPRIT做Parttime都覺得佢型, 希望ESPRIT可以快手重拾那些年的光景啦。<br />\n<br />\n曾經番生品牌亦不少: Converse, Gap, Fred Perry, Slanzenger 等等<br />\n<br />\n今天價格<br />\n思捷環球 <a href=\"http://0330.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F0330.hk&d=IZf6lr%2BCsfQX4MnErcdNIYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=57c3522d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">0330.hk</a> 12.16<br />\n<br />\n思捷環球仍是恆指成份股，乃推動恆指的選擇之一，在技術分式面來看，可見阻力如$40，$60，至於跌既空間可以話無! 所以無得輸! 現在買入，迫自己揸一兩年，收穫可數倍。"},{"pid":"26cac26dbe4a38129dd1086b43b5130d4cd8325c","tid":945566,"uid":76647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:04:12.000Z","msg":"ALLIN<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e83a67b7715f271291605a8dde52e0dd0f60f5e2","tid":945566,"uid":226713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:20:28.000Z","msg":"駁唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f04f3c42293bcd38be46465d3d2fe93a19f739e","tid":945566,"uid":44333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:33:43.000Z","msg":"垃圾公司"},{"pid":"817b43a38434a0dd6e0f7275bdadd2a2d7c5457e","tid":945566,"uid":99700,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:40:15.000Z","msg":"叫得思捷都知係垃圾啦"},{"pid":"5bfb6668f370de5600a4584dfcd75f8de9cd47da","tid":945566,"uid":143078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T04:46:06.000Z","msg":"潮流嘅野，香完就臭，臭完又香，古老當時髦，下年一定會番身，明年最樂觀可見$120，依家係白金鑽石底<br />\n一定要all in。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac80ca7d000c318b693d210352c21573e78e94c7","tid":945566,"uid":25387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18